  theme1Styles:
  - 'image_1 as photo background.

    image_2 as mascot, do not make any changes.

    image_3
    as visitor.



    Make a casual full body shot group photo of visitor and mascot
    standing above rounded star logo on the floor. Don''t change visitor face and
    retain all facial feature. Match size of visitor body height proportion with
    mascot. Relight visitor and mascot with tungsten rim light, following the background
    color and mood. Make the number of visitor is just one person, no more and no
    less. Avoid bare foot on visitor, but leave mascot bare foot.

'
  theme2Styles:
  - 'image_1 as photo background.

    image_2 as mascot, do not make any changes.

    image_3
    as visitor.



    Make a casual full body shot group photo of visitor and mascot
    standing above rounded star logo on the floor. Don''t change visitor face and
    retain all facial feature. Match size of visitor body height proportion with
    mascot. Relight visitor and mascot with tungsten rim light, following the background
    color and mood. Make the number of visitor is just one person, no more and no
    less. Avoid bare foot on visitor, but leave mascot bare foot.

'
  theme3Styles:
  - 'image_1 as photo background.

    image_2 as mascot, do not make any changes.

    image_3
    as visitor.



