    color and mood. Make the number of visitor is just one person, no more and no
    less. Avoid bare foot on visitor, but leave mascot bare foot.

'
  theme4Styles:
  - 'image_1 as photo background with mascot.

    image_2 as size comparison between
    mascot and normal human.

    image_3 as visitor.



    Make a casual full body
    shot group photo of visitor and mascot standing above rounded star logo on the
    floor. Don''t change visitor face and retain all facial feature. Make the visitors
    body size is much smaller than mascot. Relight visitor and mascot with sharp
    tungsten rim light, following the background color and mood. Make the number
    of visitor is just one person, no more and no less. Avoid bare foot on visitors,
    always make mascot''s foot in small size bare foot.

'
  theme5Styles:
  - 'image_1 as photo background.

    image_2 as mascot, do not make any changes.

    image_3
    as visitor.



    Make a casual full body shot group photo of visitor and mascot
    standing above rounded star logo on the floor. Don''t change visitor face and
    retain all facial feature. Match size of visitor body height proportion with
    mascot. Relight visitor and mascot with tungsten rim light, following the background
    color and mood. Make the number of visitor is just one person, no more and no
    less. Avoid bare foot on visitor, but leave mascot bare foot

'
  theme6Styles:
  - 'image_1 as photo background

    image_2 as group of five mascots, do not make
    any changes.

    image_3 as visitor



    Make a medium shot casual group photo
    of visitor and five mascots standing above rounded star logo on the floor. Don''t
    change visitor face and retain all facial features. Relight the visitor and mascot
    with bright keylight and tungsten rim light, following the background color and
    mood. Make the number of visitor is just one person, no more and no less. Make
    the number of mascots is five person, same as the image_2 input, no more and
    no less. Make the Singo Barong mascot always on the center, behind the visitor.
    Avoid bare foot on visitor, always make five mascots is human bare foot. Add
    camera depth of field.

'
  theme1GroupStyles:
  - 'image_1 as photo background.

    image_2 as mascot, do not make any changes.

    image_3
    as visitors.



    Make a full body shot group photo of visitors and mascot
    standing above rounded star logo on the floor. Don''t change visitors face and
    retain all facial features. Place the mascot at the center of group photo. Adjust
    the body size proportions of all subjects. Relight the visitors and mascot with
    tungsten rim light, following the background color and mood. Make the number
    of visitors same as the input image_3, no more and no less. Avoid bare foot on
    visitors, but leave mascot bare foot. Match size of visitors bodies proportion
    with mascot.

'
